					<ul>
						<li><strong>Welcome Email Series</strong> - Progressive education over first 30 days</li>
						<li><strong>Product Walkthrough Sequences</strong> - In-app guides and video tutorials</li>
						<li><strong>Training Material Delivery</strong> - Drip educational content based on progress</li>
						<li><strong>Check-In Automations</strong> - Scheduled touchpoints to ensure success</li>
						<li><strong>Task Completion Triggers</strong> - Celebrate wins when customers complete key actions</li>
						<li><strong>Onboarding Progress Tracking</strong> - Visual indicators that motivate completion</li>
					</ul>
