					<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Drive regular usage and build product habits</p>
					<p><strong>Automation Tactics:</strong></p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Usage-Based Triggers</strong> - Encourage feature adoption based on behavior</li>
						<li><strong>Feature Adoption Campaigns</strong> - Educate on underutilized features</li>
						<li><strong>Engagement Scoring</strong> - Identify highly engaged vs. at-risk customers</li>
						<li><strong>Re-Engagement Sequences</strong> - Win back inactive users automatically</li>
						<li><strong>Best Practice Tips</strong> - Automated sharing of power user strategies</li>
						<li><strong>Usage Reports</strong> - Automated dashboards showing customer progress</li>
					</ul>
					<p><strong>CRM Automation:</strong> Track product usage in your CRM to trigger personalized engagement workflows based on actual behavior, not guesswork.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="stage-box">
