					<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Prevent churn and keep customers long-term</p>
					<p><strong>Automation Tactics:</strong></p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Customer Health Scoring</strong> - Automatically identify at-risk customers</li>
						<li><strong>Churn Prevention Workflows</strong> - Intervene before customers leave</li>
						<li><strong>Renewal Reminders</strong> - Automated outreach before contract expires</li>
						<li><strong>Satisfaction Surveys</strong> - NPS and CSAT surveys at strategic moments</li>
						<li><strong>Win-Back Campaigns</strong> - Re-engage lapsed customers with special offers</li>
						<li><strong>Loyalty Program Automation</strong> - Track points, rewards, and VIP status</li>
					</ul>
					<p><a href="/services/customer-retention-systems">→ Explore CRM-based customer retention automation</a></p>
				</div>

