						<li><strong>Cross-Sell Recommendations</strong> - Suggest complementary products based on purchase history</li>
						<li><strong>Upgrade Prompts</strong> - Time-based or behavior-based upgrade offers</li>
						<li><strong>Account Expansion Workflows</strong> - Identify opportunities for multi-user or enterprise deals</li>
						<li><strong>Customer Ascension Paths</strong> - Systematically move customers up value ladder</li>
					</ul>
					<p><a href="/services/revenue-growth-automation">→ See revenue growth automation strategies</a></p>
				</div>

				<div class="stage-box">
					<h3>8. Advocacy Stage Automation</h3>
					<p><strong>Goal:</strong> Turn satisfied customers into brand champions</p>
					<p><strong>Automation Tactics:</strong></p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Review Request Automation</strong> - Ask for reviews after positive experiences</li>
						<li><strong>Referral Program Triggers</strong> - Automated invitations to refer friends</li>
						<li><strong>Testimonial Collection</strong> - Systematic gathering of customer success stories</li>
						<li><strong>Case Study Development</strong> - Automated workflows to create customer showcases</li>
						<li><strong>Loyalty Rewards</strong> - Automatically thank and reward advocates</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<h2>CRM-Based Lifecycle Automation</h2>
				<p>The most powerful lifecycle automation is built on a strong CRM foundation. Your CRM becomes the central hub that tracks customers across all stages and triggers the right automation at the right time.</p>

				<h3>What CRM Automation Enables:</h3>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Single Customer View</strong> - See entire customer journey in one place</li>
					<li><strong>Behavioral Triggers</strong> - Launch workflows based on actual customer actions</li>
					<li><strong>Segmentation</strong> - Personalize automation for different customer types</li>
					<li><strong>Multi-Channel Coordination</strong> - Orchestrate email, SMS, phone, in-app messages</li>
					<li><strong>Attribution Tracking</strong> - Know which automations drive results</li>
					<li><strong>Predictive Analytics</strong> - Forecast churn and identify upsell opportunities</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>AI Agents in Lifecycle Automation</h2>
				<p>Modern lifecycle automation includes AI agents that handle complex interactions previously requiring human touch:</p>

				<ul>
					<li><strong>AI Chatbots</strong> - Answer questions 24/7 throughout customer journey</li>
					<li><strong>AI Phone Agents</strong> - Make onboarding calls, check-ins, and follow-ups</li>
					<li><strong>AI Sales Agents</strong> - Qualify leads and schedule demos automatically</li>
					<li><strong>AI Customer Service</strong> - Resolve support issues without human intervention</li>
				</ul>
